rComments: Sarah Jayne is supportive in her teaching. She is quick to respond to any questions or emails and is thorough in her replies. She will ensure that you understand everything clearly so long as you put the effort in to ask. She is a tough APA grader, but at least you'll know that you won't make those mistakes ever again!

she's unapproachable and her lectures are dry. she changes quiz dates back and forth and it's extremely unorganized. however, her quizzes and exams are pretty fair if you understand the material. also she gives good guidance on APA formatting for her assignments. I got a good mark but didn't enjoy the course from her teaching.
